5. Git Reset
   Remove the specified file from the staging area, but leave the working directory unchanged.

     $ git reset file

     $ git reset [--soft | --mixed | --hard | --merge | --keep] <commit>

6. Git Pull

     $ git fetch

     $ git pull

7. Git Diff

    $ git diff commit1 commit2

    Example: 
      $ git diff 4b421e0cbc5ce09913a8ca2b2766f329d92f8ad4 c1674eedd37259f6ebb79f31f4e93b214c995eb0 

8. Git Clone

      $ git clone Repo_URL directory_name


